pageContext.course_type_long_description:
Explore great works of art and architecture through LEGO materials!  Collaborate in small groups to build grand structures such as the Parthenon in Greece,
the Notre Dame Cathedral in Paris, the tree houses of Papua New Guinea,
and New Yorks Empire State Building.  Follow in the footsteps of master artists with LEGO model interpretations of sculptures, mosaics, and stained glass.  Teamwork and creativity take high culture to the next level!
pageContext.course_type_name: Art and Architecture with LEGO® Materials
